Subject: Computers return after deletion
Description:
We have 6,000 available licenses and they are all used up and we should only have 4,000 computers in the environment.

Our computer number is way higher than it should be, is there a way to see when computers were onboarded so we can drill down where all of these computers came from? In addition, we have a large number of computers that have a Last Seen value of over a month ago. With our current settings they should be unlicensed, but they continue to show as licensed.
What_We_Know__c: the computers now don't even get deleted but will monitor and see if they get removed from the list
Next_Steps__c: will share a recording and an export with engineering
Solution_Comment__c:
backend procedure provided by the server team on another case also fixed this issue.
the customer confirmed ticket closure
